A Brick is the GlusterFS basic unit of storage, represented by an export
directory on a server in the trusted storage pool. A Brick is expressed
by combining a server with an export directory in the following format:

::
  _SERVER_:_EXPORT_

In the following manner:

::
  myhostname:/exports/myexportdir/

